article_id:3277,category_name:Updates,title_name:Version Update,image_path:,message:<div>Version 2.18.2, which addresses the following issue, was released around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648620000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Issue Addressed</div><div>・The adventurer Bondforged Prince&#39;s name is displayed as &quot;{player_name}&quot; on the Summon Results screen and certain details screens.</div><div><br></div><div>If you encounter this issue, please update your game to version 2.18.2.</div><div><br></div><div>■Note</div><div>It may take time for the store to reflect the updated information. Players may not be able to perform updates due to their device&#39;s data cache being full. If you are unable to perform the update, restart your device, and then try downloading it from the store.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648620000,update_time1648605417